@startuml
title Ingest 共享状态机（L2 权威图）
left to right direction

' --- 基础样式配置 ---
hide empty description
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 100

' --- 定义状态 ---
state UPLOADED
state INGESTING
state INDEXED
state FAILED
state DELETING
state DELETED

' --- 物理布局规约（关键：垂直对齐防止线条重叠） ---
' 用隐藏线强制 FAILED 在 UPLOADED 上方，DELETING 在下侧
FAILED -[hidden]-> UPLOADED
UPLOADED -[hidden]-> DELETING

' --- 1. 主流程（水平线） ---
[*] --> UPLOADED
UPLOADED -r-> INGESTING : Worker 抢占
INGESTING -r-> INDEXED : 处理成功

' --- 2. 异常流程（向上导出） ---
INGESTING -up-> FAILED : 处理失败
FAILED -left-> UPLOADED : Reprocess 成功

' --- 3. 删除流程（向下导出） ---
UPLOADED -down-> DELETING : Delete
FAILED -down-> DELETING : Delete
INDEXED -down-> DELETING : Delete

' --- 4. 结果流转 ---
DELETING -r-> DELETED : 成功
' 通过单一汇聚点描述回滚，或者指定不同侧边进入，避免线粘在一起
DELETING -up-> UPLOADED : 回滚
DELETING -up-> INDEXED : 回滚
DELETING -up-> FAILED : 回滚

' --- 5. 标注信息 ---
note top of INGESTING
  Delete/Reprocess 在
  INGESTING 阶段返回 409
end note

note bottom of DELETING
  删除失败：回滚到原状态
  (UPLOADED / FAILED / INDEXED)
end note

note right of DELETED
  重复删除幂等返回 204
end note
@enduml